  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether intravenous or oral iron are effective in
      the treatment of postoperative anemia and iron deficiency in patients submitted in
      postbariatric abdominoplasty.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
